<table cellspacing=8><tr><td valign="top">
In the traditional pieces <A HREF="gadzo.html">gadzo</A> and <A
HREF="adzogbo.html">Adzogbo</A>, the drum language helped to unite the
Eve people in their struggle against their oppressors.
<p>
<b><i>
The drum
language calls for the ancestors' support.<br>
It speaks with proverbs
in order to transmit the message with urgency.</i></b>
</p>
